      "order": 3,
      "alignment": "left",
      "body": "Per-sample QC metrics aggregated from every stage of the nf-core/viralrecon pipeline. Start here to triage which samples to drill into. The tiles are grouped into **Read QC** (fastp + Kraken2), **Alignment & Coverage** (bowtie2 + mosdepth), **Variants & Assembly** (iVar / snpEff / bcftools / QUAST), then **FastQC** sanity checks at the bottom.",
